<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Sphecodes majalis (Perez, 1903) (Manternach, specimen MNHNL 100057; BOLD identifier MNHNL 163 - 21, one middle leg was used for DNA extraction). a. Dorsal view; b. Lateral view; c. Antenna, showing flagellar segments; d. Left hind tibia, showing spines in pale pubescence; e. Tergites 4 and 5; f. Genitalia. Photos: MNHNL. Background edited using GIMP 2.8.22 (The GIMP Development Team 2020)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/501351" .

